  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether teleconsulting would be effective and
      cost-effective by reducing the patients transportations and the use of emergency units for
      nursing home residents requiring emergent or elective care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
